categories: Category:Battles of the Great Jedi Purge

nodes.text: A skirmish took place shortly after a Galactic Republic Venator-class Star Destroyer crashed on the planet Zeffo when Republic clone troopers received Order 66, a command to kill their Jedi Order commanders. Although Jedi Master Chiata and her Padawan Marseph managed to kill most of the clones of Chiata's former unit in self-defence, they were both fatally injured, with Marseph burying Chiata after her death before he too succumbed to his wounds.
